keyFacts: The FBI case 72-MM-113327 concerning Alfredo Rodriguez was initiated as a full investigation on October 28, 2009.
By December 20, 2012, the defendant Alfredo Rodriguez had been sentenced and all prosecutorial matters were resolved.
The document is an official FBI request to administratively close the case file.
